-- Alibaba finance arm, Juneyao airline both get private bank approval
-- 
-- Sun Sep 28, 2014 09:46PM EDT
-- None



BEIJING, Sept 29 (Reuters) - Alibaba Group Holding Ltd's <BABA.N> finance arm received government approval to set up a private bank, China's banking regulator said on Monday, the latest step in the e-commerce company's push into the financial services sector.

Zhejiang Ant Small & Micro Financial Services Group, an Alibaba affiliate company that contains its Alipay payment processing and financial services arm, will hold 30 percent of the bank, the regulator said.